column3: SELECT DISTINCT a.id, a.title, a.artist, a.category FROM Album a JOIN Song_in_album sia ON a.id = sia.idAlbum JOIN Song_in_playlist sip ON sia.idSong = sip.idSong JOIN Playlist p ON sip.idPlaylist = p.id WHERE p.idUser = ?;
